@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - UC007 Đăng xuất

actor "User" as Actor
boundary "SettingsUI" as UI
control "AuthController" as Controller
entity "SessionManager" as SessionDB

Actor -> UI : 1. Chọn Đăng xuất
activate UI
UI --> Actor : 2. Popup xác nhận
Actor -> UI : 3. Đồng ý
UI -> Controller : 4. logout(token)
activate Controller
Controller -> SessionDB : 5. revokeToken(token)
activate SessionDB
SessionDB --> Controller : success
deactivate SessionDB
Controller --> UI : 6. clearLocalData() & redirect
deactivate Controller
UI --> Actor : 7. Hiển thị trang Đăng nhập
deactivate UI
@enduml